abstract: When Mitt Romney shows up in Jackson Hole, Wyo., on Thursday for a reception at a country club and a more intimate dinner at the home of former Vice President Dick Cheney, the fund-raiser will represent something more than his usual tap dance for dollars.

headline.main: Fund-Raiser at Cheney Home Signals Resolve to Elect Romney
